videos.description: Bill Walton takes light-up thundersticks and gives a few drumming beats on Dave Pasch's head before the game returns to action.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Walton drums out on Pasch's dome) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Walton drums out on Pasch's dome

videos.description: Payton Pritchard knocks down the 3-pointer from NBA range giving him 17 points in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Oregon's Pritchard blazes another triple from deep) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's Pritchard blazes another triple from deep

videos.description: Josh Green starts from the corner and drives down to the bucket for a two-handed layup.

videos.description: Payton Pritchard runs around the court trying to shake off his defender, and when he finally does he drains the fadeaway triple in front of his own bench.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Oregon's Pritchard knocks down the fadeaway 3) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's Pritchard knocks down the fadeaway 3
